Interface XDIAgent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    XDIBasicAgent, XDIStandardHttpAgent, XDIStandardWebSocketAgent

    public interface XDIAgent
    An XDIAgent can intelligently construct and send XDI messages to obtain desired data.
